<p>Compila l‚Äôaplicaci√≥ HelloFX.java amb:</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>javac --module-path $PATH_TO_FX --add-modules javafx.controls HelloFX.java
